  <brief_title>Influence of Platform-switching on Bone Level Alterations: a 3 Year Randomized Clinical Trial (RCT).</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Platform-switching on Bone Level Alterations: a 3 Year RCT.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
